Bhajan: Ayodhya Ke Sita Rama Brindavan Ke Radhe Shyam
Jaya Jagadeesha Jaya Paramesha Neelakantha Sadashiva
Krishna Rama Govinda Gokula Nandana Gopala
Shyama Sundara Madana Mohana Radhe Gopal (6bt)
Vanamali Vasudeva Jagan Mohan Radha Ramana
O Bhagawan o Bhagawan Araja Suno Mere Sai Bhagawan
Radhe Krishna (2) Jai Sri Krishna Radhe (2) (6bt)
Sai Nama Bolo Govinda Naam Bolo (6bt)
Sri Rama Chandra Jaya Rama Chandra (6bt)
Deena Dukhiyon Se Prem Karo Mera Sai Prasanna Hoga
Dama Dama Dama Dama Damaru Baje... Nache Shankara Nache Re
Daya Karo Hari Narayana Kripa Karo Hey Jagavandana
Govinda Hare Gopala Hare Govinda Hare Avatara Hare
Hara Hara Shankara Samba Sada Shiva Esha Mahesha
Jai Jai Gurudeva Sri Sai Mahadeva
Rama Sri Rama Chandra Jaya (2) Rama (6bt)
Eshwaramba Priya Tanaya Eesha Mahesha Sri Saisha
Gowrivara Gangadhara Shambho Shiva Hara Bimbadhara
Devi Sai Maa Devi Saraswati Maa
Yuga Yuga ke Avatara Tumhi Ho
Gajanana Hey Gajanana Gowri Nandana Gajanana
Hey Brahma He Vishnu Daya Maya He Maheshwara
Hey Krishna Hey Krishna... Vittala Jaya Panduranga
Om Hari Om Hari Om... Bhajore Sada Om Hari Om Hari Om
Ayodhya Vasi Ram Ram (2) Dasharatha Nandana Ram
Hara Hara Hara Hara Namami Shankara Bhajamana Sai Ram
Hara Hara Hara Hara Samba Shiva
Hari Hari Sumirana Hari Hari Bhajo mana
Jaya Jagadeesha Hare Jaya Govinda Hare
Jaya Jaya Jaya Hey Gajanana Parvati Nandana
Jaya Raghu Nandana Jaya Jaya Rama
Rama Rama Jaya Raghukula Tilaka Rajeeva Lochana Ram
Shambho Mahadeva Shiva Shambho Mahadeva (Samba Sadashiva Sai Shankara)
Shivaya Nama Shiva (2) Shivaya Nama Om
Bhajo Mana Bhajo Rama Rama Ram
Hari Guna Gaan Karo Mana Mero
Sai Tere Charano Mein Koti Pranam
Daya Karo Sadguru Sai Daya Karo
Hari Hari Bhajomana Sai Ram Bhajore
Sita Ram Bolo bolo Sita Ram
Tuma Bina Prana Nahi O Sai Mere
Eshwaramba priya nandana Ratnakara kula bhushana
Govinda Hare Gopala Hare Muralidhara Hey
Hey Deena Dayalu Sai Rama Ram
Ishwara Allah Tere Naam Sai Tere Naam
Jai Santoshi Maa Jai (2) Sai Maa
Manamohana Murali Gopala Jaya Govinda Radhe Gopala
Mandira Mein Tum Ram Ho Sai
Manuva Bolo Jai Sita Rama Bolo Jai Radhe Shyam
Sai Nama Bolo Sathya Sai Naam Bolo
Sri Rama Jaya Rama Jaya (2) Rama Sri Rama Jaya Rama Sundara Nama
Sai Ram Sai Ram Gaaye Geet Sada Subah Aur Shyam
Jaya (3) Gananatha Jaya Gananatha Sri Gananatha
